data.description: *****Home qualifies for NO MONEY DOWN USDA/RD Financing!!!!*****  Welcome to home sweet home in this large ranch located on an EXTRA large lot! You definitely won't find many like this with nearly 0.78 acres, 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, dual decks, and a large detached garage with a second story! This gem has an open concept living room/dining room! The living space features vinyl flooring, tons of natural light and french doors that lead out to one of the back decks. The kitchen has been updated with fresh walls and new counters! There are so many possibilities with the large amount of room in the kitchen! The exterior features an oversized garage with a full second story! This second story is great for extra storage or finish it off and have another man cave/she shed area! There is also a huge garden on the west side of the property. Great space for growing all kinds of veggies!!!!  REMOVE SHOES WHEN SHOWING!
